The '''Septapus''' was an aquatic creature that [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] claimed, perhaps falsely, to have been attacked by. They were otherwise known to be a gentle species. They were from the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Z'trop]]. They were said to have seven tails and five glowing eyes. The species were herbivores.<ref name="MFMY">''[[Mission from Mount Yoda]]''</ref>

